span.p:
Wait switchDelay (0.3 s).
macOS silently drops back-to-back gotoSpace calls;
the gap lets each one settle before the next is dispatched.

Clear is_running — re-arm watcher.
Set is_running = false
(this is the half of the toggle we owe
after raising it for the sync-group path);
refresh lastActiveSpaces from current state;
watcher is ready for the next user switch.
